ly.";i:24;s:104:"Open your garage door release it from the automatic opener first if necessary and leave it halfway open.";i:25;s:97:"Stand back and check if it seems to be leaning to one side or if one side is lower to the ground.";i:26;s:27:"If so it needs rebalancing.";i:27;s:49:"Check the rubber strip on the bottom of the door.";i:28;s:67:"Most garage doors have a rubber strip for insulation on the bottom.";i:29;s:150:"Garage Doors and Roller Doors can if left unchecked make a lot of unnecessary noise which can be very annoying for our customers and their neighbours.";i:30;s:190:"Although it is not possible to reduce or remove all door noise due to the mechanical operation of a garage door it is possible to reduce or remove all unnecessary noise with regular general.";i:31;s:84:"Noisy garage doors are annoying but they can also be a sign that something is wrong.";i:32;s:102:"Common irritating noises are usually caused by vibrations and include grinding rattling and squeaking.";i:33;s:79:"You may even be able to hear your garage door operating while inside your home.";i:34;s:47:"Here are some tips to help you with this issue.";i:35;s:27:"Tighten all nuts and bolts.";i:36;s:80:"Read our blog on Garage Door Making Noises - Heres what Noisy Garage Door Means.";i:37;s:83:"For more information on Garage Door Repair and Garage door installation visit Door.";i:38;s:47:"Simple Steps on How to Fix a Noisy Garage Door.";i:39;s:112:"Now that you know what is causing the annoying noises from your garage door the next step is to fix the problem.";i:40;s:75:"These simple steps will help you remove the source of the unnerving noises.";i:41;s:29:"Tighten the Loose Components.";i:42;s:85:"July 9th 2019 Its only natural that your garage door will make a little bit of noise.";i:43;s:94:"It is after all a complex mechanism and mechanisms with moving parts are going to make sounds.";i:44;s:63:"However there is such thing as a garage door that is too noisy.";i:45;s:86:"If you are dealing with an excessively loud garage door you may have a bigger problem.";i:46;s:44:"Is there a way to repair a loud garage door.";i:47;s:51:"Garage doors tend to malfunction from time to time.";i:48;s:66:"Despite constant maintenance theres the factor of time playing in.";i:49;s:109:"If that is not the case then it is the lack of maintenance that is causing the door to stop working properly.";i:50;s:40:"Garage doors make a sound when it works.";i:51;s:111:"However when the noises are different from when it functions normally you should check out if theres something.";i:52;s:78:"Now garage door opener replacement and installation can range from 150 to 550.";i:53;s:113:"Having a failing garage door opener can be bothersome yet it likewise affects the safety of your family and pets.";i:54;s:116:"When something doesnt look right with your garage door call a garage door opener repair service in Clearwater today.";}}